621static inline void _nocheck__trace_qemu_loadvm_state_section(unsigned int section_type)
622{
623 if (trace_event_get_state(TRACE_QEMU_LOADVM_STATE_SECTION)) {
624 struct timeval _now;
625 gettimeofday(&_now, NULL);
626 qemu_log_mask(LOG_TRACE,
627 "%d@%zd.%06zd:qemu_loadvm_state_section " "%d" "\n",
628 getpid(),
629 (size_t)_now.tv_sec, (size_t)_now.tv_usec
630 , section_type);
631 }
632}
633
634static inline void trace_qemu_loadvm_state_section(unsigned int section_type)
635{
636 if (true) {
637 _nocheck__trace_qemu_loadvm_state_section(section_type);
638 }
639}
640
641static inline void _nocheck__trace_qemu_loadvm_state_section_command(int ret)
642{
643 if (trace_event_get_state(TRACE_QEMU_LOADVM_STATE_SECTION_COMMAND)) {
644 struct timeval _now;
645 gettimeofday(&_now, NULL);
646 qemu_log_mask(LOG_TRACE,
647 "%d@%zd.%06zd:qemu_loadvm_state_section_command " "%d" "\n",
648 getpid(),
649 (size_t)_now.tv_sec, (size_t)_now.tv_usec
650 , ret);
651 }
652}
653
654static inline void trace_qemu_loadvm_state_section_command(int ret)
655{
656 if (true) {
657 _nocheck__trace_qemu_loadvm_state_section_command(ret);
658 }
